description:
Merino warmth and comfort while on the go. This essential base layer is made with temperature regulating merino wool, so you stay warm when its cool yet won't overheat in warm weather. A nylon core keeps things light yet durable for long-lasting comfort wherever your day takes you.Made of a naturally antimicrobial merino wool blend.Nylon core for increased durability, while keeping the soft merino wool next to your skin.Slim fit for easy layering.

        Sustainability






